rows.label: tlk45340112_06_msg0001
rows.name:
We're keeping her well-maintained,
but there are no plans for the
Maelstrom to set sail any time soon.

rows.label: tlk45340112_06_msg0002
rows.name:
Well, after that nasty business with
Iira, nobody wants to be the next
person to take the Maelstrom out.

rows.label: tlk45340112_06_msg0003
rows.name:
Here's hoping when her next mission
does come along, it goes a darn sight
more smoothly than her last one!
